Pre-built binaries in different package formats can be found on

  http://www.mysql.com/downloads

You can find information about how to install MySQL Connector/ODBC at

  https://dev.mysql.com/doc/connector-odbc/en/connector-odbc-installation.html

The MySQL Connector/ODBC Reference Manual is available on

  https://dev.mysql.com/doc/connector-odbc/en/
